<codeline><highlight class="normal">UI<sp/>action<sp/>commands<sp/>and<sp/>dispatchers.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>namespace<sp/>contains<sp/>commands<sp/>for<sp/>triggering<sp/>UI<sp/>actions<sp/>and<sp/>the<sp/>dispatchers<sp/>that<sp/>route<sp/>them<sp/>to<sp/>handlers.</highlight></codeline>
