<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>Command<sp/>|<sp/>Description<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|---------|-------------|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`UiActionCommand`<sp/>|<sp/>Encapsulates<sp/>a<sp/>UI<sp/>action<sp/>request<sp/>with<sp/>source<sp/>entity<sp/>and<sp/>action<sp/>ID<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
