<codeline><highlight class="normal">updateContext.commandBuffer().add&lt;UiActionCommand&gt;(</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>menuItemEntity.entityHandle(),</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>ActionId::StartGame</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
